## Vercel Environment Variables

When deploying to Vercel, add these environment variables in the Vercel Dashboard:

1. DATABASE_URL - Your Supabase PostgreSQL connection string
2. JWT_SECRET - A random secret for JWT token signing

### How to get Supabase PostgreSQL Connection String:

1. Go to your Supabase Dashboard: https://supabase.com/dashboard
2. Select your project
3. Go to Project Settings (gear icon) > Database
4. Scroll to "Connection String" section
5. Select "URI" tab
6. Copy the connection string (it will look like):
   postgresql://postgres.[project-ref]:[YOUR-PASSWORD]@aws-0-[region].pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres
7. Replace [YOUR-PASSWORD] with your actual database password
8. Add this to Vercel as DATABASE_URL environment variable
